           move      "S"                  to   w-cnt-sts-flg-sst      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Flag di Begin non eseguito          *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-cnt-sts-flg-bgn      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Apertura files necessari alla stam- *
      *                          * pa                                  *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           perform   rou-opn-fls-000      thru rou-opn-fls-999        .
