      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       exe-fun-stp-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se files non aperti : uscita                    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-flg-opn    not  = "S"
                     go to exe-fun-stp-999.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se selezione stampante non effettuata : uscita  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-flg-sst    not  = "S"
                     go to exe-fun-stp-999.
