      *              * Se files aperti                                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-cnt-sts-flg-opn    not  = "S"
                     go to exe-fun-cls-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Chiusura files necessari alla stampa        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           perform   rou-cls-fls-000      thru rou-cls-fls-999        .
       exe-fun-cls-100.
