      *              * Page eject                                      *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se da eseguire                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-inp-mst-ejc        =    "N"
                     go to rou-stp-doc-950.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Esecuzione                                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "EJ"                 to   p-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
       rou-stp-doc-950.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Emissione sequenziale                           *
      *              *                                                 *
      *              * SIRI                                            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   rou-stp-doc-sir-000  thru rou-stp-doc-sir-999    .
       rou-stp-doc-990.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     rou-stp-doc-999.
       rou-stp-doc-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Stampa documento                                          *
