      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su codice cliente                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bit-cod-arc       not  = 0002144 and
                     rf-bit-cod-arc       not  = 0001456 and
                     rf-bit-cod-arc       not  = 0001187
                     go to rou-stp-doc-sir-900.
       rou-stp-doc-sir-100.
