      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "OO"                 to   g-ope                  .
           move      "seq "               to   g-nam                  .
           move      spaces               to   g-pat                  .
           string    w-det-pth-fso-pat
                                delimited by   spaces
                     ".CSV"     delimited by   size
                                          into g-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mcvout"
                                         using g                      .
       rou-stp-doc-sir-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
