      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bir-num-prt       not  = w-inp-mst-prt
                     go to rou-stp-doc-sir-800.
       rou-stp-doc-sir-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Incremento contatore di comodo                  *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           add       1                    to   w-stp-tes-ctr          .
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione in funzione del tipo riga            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
