      *                      * Preparazione                            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      rf-bir-dat-doc       to   s-dat                  .
           move      s-saa                to   w-wrk-dat-ann          .
           if        rf-bir-dat-doc       >    zero
                     add  1900            to   w-wrk-dat-ann          .
