      *                  * Test se posizionamento esistente            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-lpt-dat-doc-lin    =   zero or
                     w-lpt-dat-doc-pos    =   zero
                     go to stp-tes-doc-150.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Stampa                                      *
