      *              * Eventuale stampa annotazioni cliente            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           perform   stp-cor-doc-ann-000  thru stp-cor-doc-ann-999    .
       stp-cor-doc-960.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-cor-doc-999.
       stp-cor-doc-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Stampa corpo documento                                    *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Subroutine per l'assestamento posizionamenti in relazione *
      *    * alle personalizzazioni                                    *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       stp-cor-doc-app-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test sul segnale di si/no documento esso stesso *
      *              * fattura                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bit-int-ftr       =    03
                     go to stp-cor-doc-app-900.
       stp-cor-doc-app-050.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test sul segnale di si/no stampa corpo di tipo  *
      *              * 'lungo'                                         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-stb-snl        not  = "S"
                     go to stp-cor-doc-app-900.
       stp-cor-doc-app-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se richiesta la stampa corpo di tipo 'lungo'    *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       stp-cor-doc-app-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Assestamento linea per ultima riga corpo    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se a zero                          *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-lpc-ult-rig-lin    =     zero
                     go to stp-cor-doc-app-900.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Forzatura del valore                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      056                  to   w-lpc-ult-rig-lin      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Aggiustamento eventuale del valore      *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           add       w-dsp-dsp-vrt        to   w-lpc-ult-rig-lin      .
       stp-cor-doc-app-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Assestamento segnale di si/no stampa        *
      *                  * condizioni di pagamento                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test se gia' il valore indica che non   *
      *                      * devono essere stampate le condizioni di *
      *                      * pagamento                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-stp-pie-snf        =    "N"
                     go to stp-cor-doc-app-900.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Forzatura del valore a 'N'              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "N"                  to   w-stp-pie-snf          .
       stp-cor-doc-app-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-cor-doc-app-999.
       stp-cor-doc-app-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Stampa corpo documento                                    *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Subroutine per la stampa del codice prodotto              *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       stp-cor-doc-cpr-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test preliminari                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Solo se tipo prodotto P,M,S                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tip-rig-tpr        not  = "P" and
                     w-tip-rig-tpr        not  = "M" and
                     w-tip-rig-tpr        not  = "S"
                     go to stp-cor-doc-cpr-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se tipo prodotto P : solo se tipo funziona- *
      *                  * mento a spazi                               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tip-rig-tpr        =    "P"  and
                     w-tip-rig-tfu        not  = spaces
                     go to stp-cor-doc-cpr-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Solo se tipo modulo lo prevede              *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-stb-tmd        =    01
                     go to stp-cor-doc-cpr-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se posizionamento esistente            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-lpc-cod-pro-pos    =    zero
                     go to stp-cor-doc-cpr-900.
       stp-cor-doc-cpr-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione valore da stampare              *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-bir-alf-pro       to   w-stp-cor-alf-pro      .
       stp-cor-doc-cpr-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Deviazione in funzione della personalizzazione  *
      *              * relativa al codice da stampare nella colonna    *
      *              * apposita                                        *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-cds-pro        =    "C"
                     go to stp-cor-doc-cpr-400.
       stp-cor-doc-cpr-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se codice nostro : nessuna ulteriore azione     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A stampa del codice preparato               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-cor-doc-cpr-600.
       stp-cor-doc-cpr-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se codice del cliente : preparazione            *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se il tipo archivio non e' 'C' : a stampa   *
      *                  * del nostro codice                           *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bir-tip-arc       not  = "C"
                     go to stp-cor-doc-cpr-600.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se il codice per il cliente e' a spaces : a *
      *                  * stampa del nostro codice                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bir-cop-scl       =    spaces
                     go to stp-cor-doc-cpr-600.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Bufferizzazione del codice per il cliente   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      rf-bir-cop-scl       to   w-stp-cor-alf-pro      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * A stampa del codice preparato               *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-cor-doc-cpr-600.
       stp-cor-doc-cpr-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Stampa del codice preparato                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      14                   to   p-car                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
           move      w-lpc-cod-pro-pos    to   p-pos                  .
           move      w-stp-cor-alf-pro    to   p-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
       stp-cor-doc-cpr-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-cor-doc-cpr-999.
       stp-cor-doc-cpr-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Stampa corpo documento                                    *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Subroutine per la stampa della quantita' numerica         *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       stp-cor-doc-qta-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazioni preliminari                     *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione comodo per editing quanti-  *
      *                  * ta' numerica                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-stp-cor-doc-qne      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se quantita' numerica a zero : a test pre-  *
      *                  * liminari                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bir-qta-ven       =    zero
                     go to stp-cor-doc-qta-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Editing della quantita' di vendita          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "ED"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   p-tip                  .
      *
           if        rf-bir-qta-ven       >    999999
                     move  08             to   p-car
           else      move  06             to   p-car                  .
      *
           move      rf-bir-dec-qta       to   p-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   p-sgn                  .
      *
           if        rf-bir-qta-ven       >    999999
                     move  "<B"           to   p-edm
           else      move  "<GB"          to   p-edm                  .
      *
           move      rf-bir-qta-ven       to   p-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * In comodo alfabetico                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      p-edt                to   w-stp-cor-doc-qne      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Determinazione della lunghezza della quan-  *
      *                  * tita' numerica editata nella stringa alfa-  *
      *                  * betica                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-stp-cor-doc-in1      .
           move      zero                 to   w-stp-cor-doc-qll      .
           inspect   w-stp-cor-doc-qne
                                      tallying w-stp-cor-doc-in1
                                          for  trailing spaces        .
           subtract  w-stp-cor-doc-in1    from 12
                                        giving w-stp-cor-doc-qll      .
       stp-cor-doc-qta-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test preliminari                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Solo se tipo prodotto P,M,S                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tip-rig-tpr        not  = "P" and
                     w-tip-rig-tpr        not  = "M" and
                     w-tip-rig-tpr        not  = "S"
                     go to stp-cor-doc-qta-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Solo se tipo esposizione riga lo consente   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bit-int-ftr       =    01
                     go to stp-cor-doc-qta-200.
           if        rf-bir-epz-rgf       =    1 or
                     rf-bir-epz-rgf       =    2
                     go to stp-cor-doc-qta-200
           else if   rf-bir-epz-rgf       =    3
                     go to stp-cor-doc-qta-900
           else      if     rf-bir-qta-ven
                                          =    1,000
                            go to stp-cor-doc-qta-900.
       stp-cor-doc-qta-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se posizionamento esistente            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-lpc-qta-ven-pos    =    zero
                     go to stp-cor-doc-qta-900.
       stp-cor-doc-qta-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Stampa                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       stp-cor-doc-qta-420.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Se posizionamento normale                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test sulla personalizzazione che indica *
      *                      * la richiesta di allineamento a destra   *
      *                      * della quantita' numerica                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-stb-snq        not  = "S"
                     go to stp-cor-doc-qta-460.
       stp-cor-doc-qta-440.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se stampa quantita' numerica allineata  *
      *                      * a destra                                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se a zero : ad uscita               *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bir-qta-ven       =    zero
                     go to stp-cor-doc-qta-450.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Se il literal di editing e' a spa-  *
      *                          * ces : ad uscita                     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           if        w-stp-cor-doc-qne    =    spaces
                     go to stp-cor-doc-qta-450.
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Allineamento a destra quantita'     *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      12                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      w-stp-cor-doc-qne    to   w-all-str-alf          .
           perform   all-str-adx-000      thru all-str-adx-999        .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Stampa quantita' allineata a destra *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      12                   to   p-car                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
           move      w-lpc-qta-ven-pos    to   p-pos                  .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   p-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
       stp-cor-doc-qta-450.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad uscita                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-cor-doc-qta-900.
       stp-cor-doc-qta-460.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Se stampa quantita' numerica allineata  *
      *                      * in modo normale                         *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "N"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      07                   to   p-car                  .
           move      rf-bir-dec-qta       to   p-dec                  .
           move      "S"                  to   p-sgn                  .
           move      "GB"                 to   p-edm                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
           move      w-lpc-qta-ven-pos    to   p-pos                  .
           subtract  2                    from p-pos                  .
           move      rf-bir-qta-ven       to   p-num                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Ad uscita                               *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-cor-doc-qta-900.
       stp-cor-doc-qta-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-cor-doc-qta-999.
       stp-cor-doc-qta-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Stampa corpo documento                                    *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Subroutine per la stampa numero di telefono del cliente   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       stp-cor-doc-tlc-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test preliminari                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su posizionamento                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-lpc-des-pro-pos    =    zero
                     go to stp-cor-doc-tlc-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su personalizzazione stampa numero di  *
      *                  * telefono                                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-snx-tel        not  = "S"
                     go to stp-cor-doc-tlc-900.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su valore del campo                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-stp-tes-dcc-tel    =    spaces
                     go to stp-cor-doc-tlc-900.
       stp-cor-doc-tlc-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su righe corpo residue                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        p-lnr                <    w-lpc-ult-rig-lin
                     go to stp-cor-doc-tlc-200.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Reintestazione documento                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   rei-mod-tes-000      thru rei-mod-tes-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su status di uscita                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-out-mst-stp        =    spaces
                     go to stp-cor-doc-tlc-200.
           move      spaces               to   w-out-mst              .
           perform   wrt-out-mst-000      thru wrt-out-mst-999        .
           go to     stp-cor-doc-tlc-900.
       stp-cor-doc-tlc-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Preparazione literal                        *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      03                   to   w-all-str-num          .
           move      40                   to   w-all-str-lun          .
           move      "(Telefono:"         to   w-all-str-cat (1)      .
           move      w-stp-tes-dcc-tel    to   w-all-str-cat (2)      .
           move      ")"                  to   w-all-str-cat (3)      .
           perform   all-str-cat-000      thru all-str-cat-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Interlinea                                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "LF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Stampa                                      *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   p-car                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
           move      w-lpc-des-pro-pos    to   p-pos                  .
           move      w-all-str-alf        to   p-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
       stp-cor-doc-tlc-900.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Uscita                                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           go to     stp-cor-doc-tlc-999.
       stp-cor-doc-tlc-999.
           exit.

      *    *===========================================================*
      *    * Stampa corpo documento                                    *
      *    *                                                           *
      *    * Subroutine per la stampa dicitura per lettera d'intenti   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       stp-cor-doc-lic-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test preliminari                                *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se da stampare                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Solo se bolla/fattura                   *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bit-int-ftr       not  = 03
                     go to stp-cor-doc-lic-900.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su posizionamento                  *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-lpc-des-pro-pos    =    zero
                     go to stp-cor-doc-lic-900.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test personalizzazione gestione lettere *
      *                      * d'intenti clienti                       *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-prs-lic-snx        not  = "S"
                     go to stp-cor-doc-lic-900.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su Assoggettamento iva cliente     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if not   (rf-bit-ass-iva       >    300 and
                     rf-bit-ass-iva       <    700   )
                     go to stp-cor-doc-lic-900.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Lettura record [lic]                    *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           move      "RK"                 to   f-ope                  .
           move      "CODCLI"             to   f-key                  .
           move      rf-bit-cod-arc       to   rf-lic-cod-cli         .
           move      "pgm/cge/fls/ioc/obj/ioflic"
                                          to   s-pat                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mfiltp"
                                         using s                      .
           call      s-pat               using f
                                               rf-lic                 .
           if        f-sts                not  = e-not-err
                     go to stp-cor-doc-lic-900.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Controllo che data documento rientri    *
      *                      * entro gli estermi lettera d'intenti     *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        rf-bit-dat-doc       <    rf-lic-drf-ini or
                     rf-bit-dat-doc       >    rf-lic-drf-fin
                     go to stp-cor-doc-lic-900.
       stp-cor-doc-lic-200.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su righe corpo residue                 *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-lpc-ult-rig-lin    to   w-stp-cor-doc-c01      .
           subtract  6                    from w-stp-cor-doc-c01      .
           if        p-lnr                <    w-stp-cor-doc-c01
                     go to stp-cor-doc-lic-100.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Reintestazione documento                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           perform   rei-mod-tes-000      thru rei-mod-tes-999        .
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Test su status di uscita                *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
           if        w-out-mst-stp        =    spaces
                     go to stp-cor-doc-lic-100.
           move      spaces               to   w-out-mst              .
           perform   wrt-out-mst-000      thru wrt-out-mst-999        .
           go to     stp-cor-doc-lic-900.
       stp-cor-doc-lic-100.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Interlinea vuota                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "LF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Stampa dicitura                             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Prima riga                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Interlinea                          *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "LF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Stampa                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   p-car                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
           move      w-lpc-des-pro-pos    to   p-pos                  .
           if        rf-lic-alx-exp       =    spaces
                     move  "Fatturazione non imponibile iva ai sensi"
                                          to   p-alf
           else      move  rf-lic-alx-exp to   p-alf                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
       stp-cor-doc-lic-200.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Seconda riga                            *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Interlinea                          *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "LF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Stampa                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
           move      40                   to   p-car                  .
           move      p-lnr                to   p-lin                  .
           move      w-lpc-des-pro-pos    to   p-pos                  .
      *
           if        rf-lic-alx-exp       =    spaces
                     move  "dell'Art. 8 Lettera c del D.P.R. 633/72."
                                          to   p-alf
           else      move  rf-lic-alx-exp
                          (41 : 26)       to   p-alf                  .
      *
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
       stp-cor-doc-lic-300.
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                      * Terza riga                              *
      *                      *-----------------------------------------*
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Interlinea                          *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "LF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/mprint"
                                         using p                      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Composizione stringa                *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-stp-cor-doc-rif      .
           move      1                    to   w-stp-cor-doc-pnt      .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Literal                         *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           string    "(Vs. lettera d'intenti numero "
                                delimited by   size
                                          into w-stp-cor-doc-rif
                                  with pointer w-stp-cor-doc-pnt      .
      *                              *---------------------------------*
      *                              * Numero lettera d'intenti        *
      *                              *---------------------------------*
           string    rf-lic-num-lic
                                delimited by   spaces
                                          into w-stp-cor-doc-rif
                                  with pointer w-stp-cor-doc-pnt      .
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
      *                          * Stampa                              *
      *                          *-------------------------------------*
           move      "PF"                 to   p-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   p-tip                  .
